_sText:
Welcome to surf AKRON NOOBS.  Thats right!  This map was made with the surfers of Akron in mind.  Basically so when they, well a select few, will get either overly frustrated or just cry when they decide to surf it!

Otherwise besides that bit of input, it is a moderate surf with a few secrets nothing major though. 

Just a fun map for surfers of all levels.  Honestly though, if you are a noob surfer, don't even try.

Enjoy. 

(Comments on the map itself please.  How the surf is/what could be change/added etc.)
